      1          /**
      2           *  @file       
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Implements the interfaces for regulations. Some interfaces can be used on both ACU and HMI. Some interfaces
      5           *              are meant for only ACU or only HMI.
      6           *
      7           *  @details    Common interfaces:
      8           *              - Get the position of regulation
      9           *              - Get number of regulations defined in the setting file
     10           *              - Get number of regulations that are "to main" (considered by ACU)
     11           *              - Get configuration of a regulation (function ID or other behavioral flags)
     12           *              - Get current index of regulations
     13           *
     14           *              ACU only interfaces:
     15           *              - Accept/Reject regulations
     16           *              - Check if a regulation has changed (new request from HMI)
     17           *              - Get main values of a regulation
     18           *              - Get main value type
     19           *
     20           *              HMI only interfaces:
     21           *              - Register a callback function on regulation changes
     22           *              - Set regulation request
     23           *              - Get visual values of a regulation
     24           *              - Get visual value type
     25           *
     26           *  @copyright  Copyright 2015-2019 Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     27           */
